headline: FareStart Receives $450,000 Grant From KeyBank Foundation
summary: The KeyBank Foundation has announced a grant of $450,000 to FareStart as the nonprofit seeks to extend the breadth and depth of its job training programs, with a goal of increasing overall program impact by 60% over three years. Funds from the KeyBank ...
